snippet.title: Super Mega Space Blaster Special Turbo - Announcement Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: The easy to play hard to master space blaster Super Mega Space Blaster Special Turbo launches on January 14 2020. Save humanity and become the greatest space blaster pilot in this frantic retro inspired space shooter.
